msgstr ""

#: includes/abilities.php:2544
msgid "Writes a structured-data schema block (e.g. FAQPage, Article, Product) to a Rank Math schema meta key. The schema_data object is sanitized and stored as a PHP-serialized array, exactly as Rank Math expects, so it renders as JSON-LD in <head>. Use this to add or replace a schema block on any post or page."
msgstr ""

